entries.s_12: Well you seem ok. What do you want?
entries.s_16: Well isn't that something. That so-called friend of mine just left me to fend for my self while he hides out. Protect him from the bounty hunter he said. Protect yourself I say.
entries.s_18: Some information on your friend, Untas.
entries.s_19: Yea and what do I get for this information?
entries.s_20: I got some dar'kal spice in my pack.
entries.s_21: Dar'kal? Hmmm ... well if you take it out of your pack and give it over I might talk.
entries.s_23: Yes you do. So tell me where he is.
entries.s_25: You need to take care of Untas.
entries.s_26: He's at that White Thranta place. Trying to blend in with the Thranta people, or something. Said I should guard him. Well forget that. I ain't taking a fall for him.
entries.s_32: Does a wretched hive of scum and villainy mean anything to you? Get lost!
entries.s_9: I haven't seen Untas in a while. I assume you took care of him?
